<ab> <title>XIII.  HVMNVS DE PENTECOSTE. </title> </ab>
          <l n="1"><milestone unit="para"/>Et hoc supernum munus est,  </l>
            <l n="2"><choice><sic>Qnod</sic><corr>Quod</corr></choice> lingua linguis militat.  </l> 

          <l n="3"><milestone unit="para"/>Quis non tonantis praemia  </l>
            <l n="4">Per dona eiusdem proferat?  </l> 

          <l n="5"><milestone unit="para"/> Facit <choice><sic>toquendo</sic><corr>loquendo</corr></choice> qui sapit,   </l>
            <l n="6">Dignum loquatur ut deo.  </l> 

          <l n="7"><milestone unit="para"/>Infundit <choice><sic>eece</sic><corr>ecce</corr></choice> spiritus,  </l>
            <l n="8">Et ora rursus instruit.  </l> 

          <l n="9"><milestone unit="para"/>Intrat <choice><sic>neterno</sic><corr>ueterno</corr></choice> pectora  </l>
             <l n="10">Euiscerata nubilo.  </l>
 
          <l n="11"><milestone unit="para"/>In hoc <choice><sic>apostoUs</sic><corr>apostolis</corr></choice> die  </l>
            <l n="12">Dum uerba Verbum diuidit,  </l>
            <l n="13">Sermone mundi praepotens  </l>
            <l n="14">Et corda mundi contulit.  </l> 

          <l n="15"><milestone unit="para"/> Summis feratur laudibus:   </l>
            <l n="16">Habet homo ora gentium,  </l>
            <l n="17">Thrax Gallus Indus unus est.  </l> 

          <l n="18"><milestone unit="para"/>Quod blanda ludit Graecia,  </l>
            <l n="19">Quod saeuit atrox <choice><sic>bsrbarum</sic><corr>barbarum</corr></choice>  </l>
             <l n="20">Stridor Canopi murmuris,   </l>
            <l n="21">Quod lingua latrat Parthica,  </l>
            <l n="22">Pectus repleuit hospitum.  </l> 

          <l n="23"><milestone unit="para"/>Mundi ad <choice><sic>salvtem</sic><corr>salutem</corr></choice> curritur  </l>
            <l n="24"><sic>Nolente</sic> mundo tot uiis,  </l>


